702104f-a.title: Bronx: Westchester Avenue - St. Ann's Avenue
702104f-a.text:
B75 and 577 Wastchester Avenue (elevated thereon), at, and
adjoining the N.E. corner of St. Anns Avenue, showing two old frame
buildings with stucco fronts. The elevated is that of the I.R.T.
Pelham Bay Park subway line.
June 25, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
